"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(*)\nFROM account\nJOIN loan ON account.account_id = loan.account_id\nWHERE account.frequency = 'POPLATEK TYDNE' AND loan.amount < 200000;\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the number of accounts with a weekly issuance frequency (`POPLATEK TYDNE`) that have a loan amount of less than 200,000. It joins the `account` and `loan` tables using the `account_id` foreign key relationship."